          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The samples were made by using powders of GeO2(99.99%),",
                "As2O3(99.8%) and SeO2 (99%), with aluminum as monitor",
                "element. A number of aluminum thin foils, each of size",
                "10 mm x10 mm, were obtained by cutting a pure aluminum",
                "foil of thickness ~0.2 mm. After making twenty pairs of",
                "these aluminum foils, weight of each pair was measured",
                "with an accuracy of +- 10 microgram.",
                "Each sample was prepared by sandwiching a known weight",
                "of element between two aluminum foils, and then packing",
                "in a polyethylene bag.",
                "By folding the polyethylene bag,the sample size was",
                "made close to 10 mm x 10 mm. Following this procedure,",
                "nine samples each of (i) germanium (ii) arsenic",
                "and(iii) selenium,with aluminum as monitor element,",
                "were made and used in the present experiment."
              ]
            }
          ],
